      "text": "They use maps to collaborate and co-ordinate. The problem in business is the lack of a common language i.e. the lack of any form of mapping. If you can’t map what you are doing, then I recommend you hold back from acting and spend a few hours mapping it. [https://book.wardleymaps.com/notes/Use+a+common+language page]"
